{
  "stem": "16106.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We'll take your children to the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Threw them into the truck like footballs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember, I saw [INAUDIBLE] taking warm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They dressed them [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Had to bring them, dress them up warmly, and they walked them out to a children [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One of the policeman, [INAUDIBLE] he was, he had a bad reputation already what before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he was a-- he stole allegedly, the sugar from the, from the shop.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they had their order to look for the thief.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was among, you know, all the [INAUDIBLE], and he was among the one who looked for the thief.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they found out it's him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was taken out and he was executed on his own.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was always more dramatic when, when one was executed on one's own.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, a special execution.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] Like before the ghetto, in the beginning, we used to go into hiding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they, and the Germans grabbed two girls who were from my school and they had to go about in masks and point them out under pressure and blackmail and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then they were executed on their own after they [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Which is always has a special eerie, yucky feeling about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was executed on his own.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those things have happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we could have managed in the ghetto because we still had our contacts where we could exchange things for food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- especially my mom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Went to work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People and Latvians were, were bringing some, some potatoes for, for, for a ring.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mom was, Mama was, knew how to make nothing from-- potato, potato kugel for, from anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, she used to make and do it from-- I don't know what she made it from.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
